{"tid":1801494,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【享年73歲】一代禁片《一樹梨花壓海棠》(Lolita) 女星蘇麗安 (Sue Lyon) 病逝","createTime":"2019-12-28T16:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T06:03:04.000Z","uid":35221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ff8baaf9ab205437fee74dd473040eaca88863","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:17:40.000Z","msg":"2019年12月28日<br />\n【享年73歲】一代禁片《一樹梨花壓海棠》女星蘇麗安病逝<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1228 12:54<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509063_8c20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509063_8c20.jpg&h=7adb57c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇麗安於前日逝世，享年73歲。<br />\n<br />\n1962年電影《一樹梨花壓海棠》（Lolita）女星Sue Lyon（蘇麗安）前日逝世，享年73歲。據美國《紐約時報》（New York Times）指，蘇麗安於洛杉磯病逝，其好友Phil Syracopoulos指蘇麗安病了一段時間，但就未有公佈致死原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509269_5d21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509269_5d21.jpg&h=0de0d690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一樹梨花壓海棠》成為經典電影。<br />\n<br />\n蘇麗安1946年出生，於13歲做模特兒出道，於翌年參演已故電影大師史丹利寇比力克（Stanley Kubrick）執導的《一樹梨花壓海棠》投身電影圈，當時她擊敗800多名對手爭贏女主角一職，並憑Lolita一角奪得《金球獎》（Golden Globe Awards）獲得新人獎，該片因內容敏感曾被列為禁片，Lolita亦成了孌童的代名詞。蘇麗安過去曾經有過五段婚姻，當中包括81歲《2020》（Blade Runner）科幻電影編劇漢普敦芬奇（Hampton Fancher），兩人於1965年離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509931_d3aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509931_d3aa.jpg&h=f1b5dcce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一樹梨花壓海棠》當年在香港上映時的報紙廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509492_0435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509492_0435.jpg&h=c5353984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇麗安與《一》片男主角James Mason演對手戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509492_77b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509492_77b2.jpg&h=68d5cb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘇麗安憑1962年電影《一樹梨花壓海棠》一炮而紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577522442_2c58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577522442_2c58.jpg&h=1793ba0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577522442_494a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577522442_494a.jpg&h=0c029a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一樹梨花壓海棠》劇照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191228/large/1577509852_5bee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191228%2Flarge%2F1577509852_5bee.jpg&h=3b06903a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漢普敦芬奇（Hampton Fancher）與蘇麗安於1965年離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191228/60425867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60425867&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=175c119e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191228%2F60425867&h=0739a0b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191228/60425867</a>"},{"pid":"95c6df81a64bb36b6266c4cf423d03e0593cb5ad","tid":1801494,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800386</a>"},{"pid":"bf11a59c754398625c62f4261c2c7066c2a7c85a","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"《一樹梨花壓海棠》預告片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihZ-aIJj6-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DihZ-aIJj6-g&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=8c18dae0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihZ-aIJj6-g</a>"},{"pid":"7c929689a936fae4ba18a4360b98a2f734401aad","tid":1801494,"uid":221773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6173155857fbb522dbb2cbe792b3a3ba113c8e","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c929689a936fae4ba18a4360b98a2f734401aad","tid":1801494,"uid":221773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:53:37.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae7b4d4dcdf44efa25711defb46487a31f242b5","tid":1801494,"uid":236359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"未睇Stanley kubrick 呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a27377aca8e4141968ffad3c1f056dabdce27e3","tid":1801494,"uid":45749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"我嘅性啟蒙老師"},{"pid":"d215c6045d0cea37dca75f20c21559be070649a5","tid":1801494,"uid":20282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"佢好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8590b31e086b93adb255bf2fc2aaf77f2872f5b1","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a27377aca8e4141968ffad3c1f056dabdce27e3","tid":1801494,"uid":45749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"我嘅性啟蒙老師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff63ef4c7b6cab171a33b1587abf8b63e6c173a2","tid":1801494,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4260d24dc4048f3fa27490571b8a6a958f67532","tid":1801494,"uid":237227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232f89b442c72b89c1c6ed7e5834eca3452219f3","tid":1801494,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"當年出到呢種題材真係好CLS<br />\nBTW chloe moretz 好似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有令我回想講故台既二家姐故<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182eed37cb4b978ddb4df4cf90bd00e8ebe30427","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232f89b442c72b89c1c6ed7e5834eca3452219f3","tid":1801494,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"當年出到呢種題材真係好CLS<br />\nBTW chloe moretz 好似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有令我回想講故台既二家姐故<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寇比力克實在係天才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d51755805f5922e7f8999b0be3a0c86a05f16b","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"個戲名真係改得好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d43d5e755f8537932b7d562f6fb797ee735ea6a","tid":1801494,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"張海報唔講咩導演既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78674b52116050fc588aaa4eb0441013f5f2f65d","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"f2d51755805f5922e7f8999b0be3a0c86a05f16b","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"個戲名真係改得好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"證明咗上一代啲人係有文化啲，將一句古代民間詩句愛嚟改做戲名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句嘢而家最廣泛流傳個來源版本係一首絕句：<br />\n<br />\n十八新娘八十郎，蒼蒼白髮對紅妝。<br />\n鴛鴦被裡成雙夜，<strong>一樹梨花壓海棠</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n呢首絕句曾經謠傳話係蘇東坡作畀老友張先話佢臨老入花叢。有學者考證過，其實原文係嚟自明代筆記小說入面一啲民間詩句。最早一種版本見於明代蔣一葵《堯山堂外紀》卷97「王寵」條，提到一個明代書畫家王寵寫過一首詩講人臨老入花叢，入面補充嗰陣就有講「<strong>一朵梨花壓海棠</strong>」：<br />\n<br />\n王寵〔顧璘：字履吉，號雅宜，蘇州人。嘉靖間貢士，清夷恬曠，與物無兢，人擬之黃叔度云。〕<br />\n<br />\n王雅宜〈嘲六十再娶〉詩云：「六十作新郎，殘花入洞房。聚猶秋燕子，健亦病鴛鴦。戲水全無力，銜泥不上樑。空煩神女意，為雨傍高唐。」（蔣一葵：浙人有嘲年六十三娶十六歲女為繼室者云：「二八佳人七九郎，婚姻何故不相當。紅綃帳裡求歡處，<strong>一朵梨花壓海棠</strong>。」）<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇軾的確作過一首詩畀張先講佢臨老入花叢呢單嘢，首詩係〈張子野年八十五，尚聞買妾，述古令作詩〉 ：<br />\n<br />\n錦里先生自笑狂，莫欺九尺鬢眉蒼。<br />\n詩人老去鶯鶯在，公子歸來燕燕忙。<br />\n柱下相君猶有齒，江南刺史已無腸。<br />\n平生謬作安昌客，略遣彭宣到後堂。<br />\n<br />\n至於張先和作而家得返兩句殘句，見於宋代葉夢得《石林詩話》：<br />\n<br />\n愁似鰥魚知夜永，懶同蝴蝶為春忙。"},{"pid":"cf4732c6c344408f5b55464e3a91407584240f5d","tid":1801494,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182eed37cb4b978ddb4df4cf90bd00e8ebe30427","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232f89b442c72b89c1c6ed7e5834eca3452219f3","tid":1801494,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"當年出到呢種題材真係好CLS<br />\nBTW chloe moretz 好似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有令我回想講故台既二家姐故<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寇比力克實在係天才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"改篇自小說架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad895493aa99df60e1affd744d568b1f838dd585","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf4732c6c344408f5b55464e3a91407584240f5d","tid":1801494,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182eed37cb4b978ddb4df4cf90bd00e8ebe30427","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"232f89b442c72b89c1c6ed7e5834eca3452219f3","tid":1801494,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"當年出到呢種題材真係好CLS<br />\nBTW chloe moretz 好似佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有令我回想講故台既二家姐故<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n寇比力克實在係天才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"改篇自小說架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"我話佢導演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01979abc130c168f62ef5d2a5677c5fc91276a3e","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2d43d5e755f8537932b7d562f6fb797ee735ea6a","tid":1801494,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"張海報唔講咩導演既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"都係唔同戲會有唔同，我搵過一啲舊報紙都係冇寫寇比力克個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNzE7Hc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNzE7Hc.jpg&h=73cdd6ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qUYDOT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qUYDOT.jpg&h=609b82fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69c2877ecb42b7b1f8e960301da6297772156d4f","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78674b52116050fc588aaa4eb0441013f5f2f65d","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"f2d51755805f5922e7f8999b0be3a0c86a05f16b","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"個戲名真係改得好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"證明咗上一代啲人係有文化啲，將一句古代民間詩句愛嚟改做戲名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句嘢而家最廣泛流傳個來源版本係一首絕句：<br />\n<br />\n十八新娘八十郎，蒼蒼白髮對紅妝。<br />\n鴛鴦被裡成雙夜，<strong>一樹梨花壓海棠</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n呢首絕句曾經謠傳話係蘇東坡作畀老友張先話佢臨老入花叢。有學者考證過，其實原文係嚟自明代筆記小說入面一啲民間詩句。最早一種版本見於明代蔣一葵《堯山堂外紀》卷97「王寵」條，提到一個明代書畫家王寵寫過一首詩講人臨老入花叢，入面補充嗰陣就有講「<strong>一朵梨花壓海棠</strong>」：<br />\n<br />\n王寵〔顧璘：字履吉，號雅宜，蘇州人。嘉靖間貢士，清夷恬曠，與物無兢，人擬之黃叔度云。〕<br />\n<br />\n王雅宜〈嘲六十再娶〉詩云：「六十作新郎，殘花入洞房。聚猶秋燕子，健亦病鴛鴦。戲水全無力，銜泥不上樑。空煩神女意，為雨傍高唐。」（蔣一葵：浙人有嘲年六十三娶十六歲女為繼室者云：「二八佳人七九郎，婚姻何故不相當。紅綃帳裡求歡處，<strong>一朵梨花壓海棠</strong>。」）<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇軾的確作過一首詩畀張先講佢臨老入花叢呢單嘢，首詩係〈張子野年八十五，尚聞買妾，述古令作詩〉 ：<br />\n<br />\n錦里先生自笑狂，莫欺九尺鬢眉蒼。<br />\n詩人老去鶯鶯在，公子歸來燕燕忙。<br />\n柱下相君猶有齒，江南刺史已無腸。<br />\n平生謬作安昌客，略遣彭宣到後堂。<br />\n<br />\n至於張先和作而家得返兩句殘句，見於宋代葉夢得《石林詩話》：<br />\n<br />\n愁似鰥魚知夜永，懶同蝴蝶為春忙。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"以前真係好有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁深嘅戲名都一改就知道內容係咩"},{"pid":"68257aacc3477fa1207d074abb0f664b4728a76f","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"69c2877ecb42b7b1f8e960301da6297772156d4f","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78674b52116050fc588aaa4eb0441013f5f2f65d","tid":1801494,"uid":35221,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"f2d51755805f5922e7f8999b0be3a0c86a05f16b","tid":1801494,"uid":106336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"個戲名真係改得好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:17:52.000Z","msg":"證明咗上一代啲人係有文化啲，將一句古代民間詩句愛嚟改做戲名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢句嘢而家最廣泛流傳個來源版本係一首絕句：<br />\n<br />\n十八新娘八十郎，蒼蒼白髮對紅妝。<br />\n鴛鴦被裡成雙夜，<strong>一樹梨花壓海棠</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n呢首絕句曾經謠傳話係蘇東坡作畀老友張先話佢臨老入花叢。有學者考證過，其實原文係嚟自明代筆記小說入面一啲民間詩句。最早一種版本見於明代蔣一葵《堯山堂外紀》卷97「王寵」條，提到一個明代書畫家王寵寫過一首詩講人臨老入花叢，入面補充嗰陣就有講「<strong>一朵梨花壓海棠</strong>」：<br />\n<br />\n王寵〔顧璘：字履吉，號雅宜，蘇